          <span class="byline-author">By <strong><a href="/commentary/rrm-spotlight-naomi-whittaker-md/">Dr. Naomi Whittaker, MD, Board-Certified OBGYN, MIGS, NFPMC, FCI</a></strong></span>
          <LastUpdated path={PAGE_PATH} class="byline-date" />
        </div>
      </div>

